    <entry>
      <title>标签外挂(修改文章样式结构)</title>
      <link href="/2022/08/26/tagPlugins/"/>
      <url>/2022/08/26/tagPlugins/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="标签外挂"><a href="#标签外挂" class="headerlink" title="标签外挂"></a>标签外挂</h1><div class="note blue info flat"><p>标签外挂是Hexo独有的功能，并不是标准的Markdown格式。以下的写法，只适用于Butterfly主题，用在其它主题上不会有效果，甚至可能会报错。使用前请留意</p></div><div class="note orange warning flat"><p>​标签外挂虽然能为主题带来一些额外的功能和UI方面的强化，但是，标签外挂也有明显的限制，使用时请留意。</p></div><h2 id="注释-Note"><a href="#注释-Note" class="headerlink" title="注释(Note)"></a>注释(Note)</h2><ol><li><p>第一种是Hexo自带的Note通用设置</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">note:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Note tag style values:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - simple    bs-callout old alert style. Default.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - modern    bs-callout new (v2-v3) alert style.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - flat      flat callout style with background, like on Mozilla or StackOverflow.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - disabled  disable all CSS styles import of note tag.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">style:</span> <span class="string">simple</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">icons:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">border_radius:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Offset lighter of background in % for modern and flat styles (modern: -12 | 12; flat: -18 | 6).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Offset also applied to label tag variables. This option can work with disabled note tag.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">light_bg_offset:</span> <span class="number">0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>自定义Note</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note [color] [no-icon] [style] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">Any content (想要输出的内容)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">或</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note [color] [icon] [style] %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">Any content (想要输出的内容)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">属性</th><th align="center">用法</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">color</td><td align="center">配色（default &#x2F; primary &#x2F; success &#x2F; info &#x2F; warning &#x2F; danger&#x2F; blue &#x2F; pink &#x2F; red &#x2F; purple &#x2F; orange &#x2F; green）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">no-icon</td><td align="center">不显示icon</td></tr><tr><td align="center">icon</td><td align="center">显示icon且可自定义icon（仅支持<a href="http://www.fontawesome.com.cn/faicons/">fontawesome</a> 图标, 也可以配置 no-icon，默认有default,primary,success,info,warning,danger）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">style</td><td align="center">覆盖配置中的样式（simple&#x2F;modern&#x2F;flat&#x2F;disabled）</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="note blue info flat"><p>案列如下：   </p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note info simple %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note info modern %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note info flat %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note info disabled %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note info no-icon %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">或</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; simple %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; modern %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; flat %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; disabled %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue no-icon %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note info simple"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note info modern"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note info flat"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note info disabled"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note info no-icon flat"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div><div class="note blue icon-padding modern"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div><div class="note blue icon-padding flat"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div><div class="note blue icon-padding disabled"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div><div class="note blue no-icon flat"><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div></li></ol><h2 id="相册图库-galleryGroup-amp-gallery"><a href="#相册图库-galleryGroup-amp-gallery" class="headerlink" title="相册图库(galleryGroup&amp;gallery)"></a>相册图库(galleryGroup&amp;gallery)</h2><h2 id="隐藏与显示-tag-hide"><a href="#隐藏与显示-tag-hide" class="headerlink" title="隐藏与显示(tag-hide)"></a>隐藏与显示(tag-hide)</h2><h2 id="绘图-mermaid"><a href="#绘图-mermaid" class="headerlink" title="绘图(mermaid)"></a>绘图(mermaid)</h2><h2 id="标签页-tabs"><a href="#标签页-tabs" class="headerlink" title="标签页(tabs)"></a>标签页(tabs)</h2><h2 id="按钮-button"><a href="#按钮-button" class="headerlink" title="按钮(button)"></a>按钮(button)</h2><h2 id="内联图片-inlineImg"><a href="#内联图片-inlineImg" class="headerlink" title="内联图片(inlineImg)"></a>内联图片(inlineImg)</h2><h2 id="高亮文字-label"><a href="#高亮文字-label" class="headerlink" title="高亮文字(label)"></a>高亮文字(label)</h2><h2 id="时间线-步骤条-timeline"><a href="#时间线-步骤条-timeline" class="headerlink" title="时间线(步骤条)(timeline)"></a>时间线(步骤条)(timeline)</h2><h2 id="链接-flink"><a href="#链接-flink" class="headerlink" title="链接(flink)"></a>链接(flink)</h2>]]></content>
      
      
      
